  "keyFeatures": [
    "Safe, idiomatic Rust wrappers around the libgbm C library",
    "Reference-counted Device, BufferObject, and Surface types with automatic lifetime management",
    "Buffer import from Wayland buffers, EGL images, and DMA-BUF file descriptors",
    "Optional integration with drm-rs for direct KMS/DRM framebuffer operations",
    "Support for format modifiers (tiling, compression) via explicit modifier APIs",
    "CPU-accessible buffer mapping with read and read/write transfer modes",
    "Serde serialization support for BufferObjectFlags via optional feature flag",
    "Thread-safe (Send + Sync) types backed by atomic reference counting"
  ],
